# CLAUDE.md

This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.

本文件为 Claude Code (claude.ai/code) 提供在此代码库中工作的指导。

---

## Project Overview / 项目概述

This is an implementation of **Instant Policy: In-Context Imitation Learning via Graph Diffusion** (ICLR 2025). The project uses graph diffusion models for in-context imitation learning, with a complete ShapeNet pseudo-demonstration generation system following the paper's Appendix D specifications.

这是 **Instant Policy: In-Context Imitation Learning via Graph Diffusion** (ICLR 2025) 的实现。项目使用图扩散模型进行上下文模仿学习，包含完整的 ShapeNet 伪演示生成系统，严格遵循论文附录 D 的规范。

**Key Components / 核心组件:**
- Graph diffusion model (AGI) for policy learning / 图扩散模型用于策略学习
- ShapeNet-based pseudo-demonstration generation / 基于 ShapeNet 的伪演示生成
- RLBench simulation environment for evaluation / RLBench 仿真环境用于评估
- PyTorch Lightning training framework with PyTorch Geometric / 使用 PyTorch Geometric 的 PyTorch Lightning 训练框架

