## Development Commands / 开发命令

### Environment Setup / 环境设置

```bash
# Activate conda environment / 激活 conda 环境
conda activate ip_env

# Install package in development mode (if needed) / 开发模式安装（如需要）
pip install -e .
```

### Training / 训练

**Continuous generation (recommended, paper approach) / 连续生成（推荐，论文方法）:**

```bash
# Quick test (1K samples) / 快速测试（1K 样本）
python train_with_pseudo.py --run_name=test --num_pseudo_samples=1000 --buffer_size=100

# Full scale (700K samples, paper setting) / 完整规模（700K 样本，论文设置）
python train_with_pseudo.py --run_name=full_scale --num_pseudo_samples=700000 --buffer_size=2000 --record=1
```

**Pre-generated data / 预生成数据:**

```bash
# Generate data first / 先生成数据
python generate_pseudo_data.py --num_tasks=1000 --output_dir=./data/pseudo_train --num_workers=4

# Train with pre-generated data / 使用预生成数据训练
python ip/train.py --run_name=my_experiment --data_path_train=./data/pseudo_train --data_path_val=./data/val --record=1
```

**Fine-tuning (PD++ setup) / 微调（PD++ 设置）:**

```bash
python train_with_pseudo.py --fine_tune=1 --model_path=./checkpoints --real_data_path=./data/rlbench --real_data_ratio=0.5
```

### Testing and Evaluation / 测试与评估

**Simulation deployment / 仿真部署:**

```bash
# Basic evaluation / 基础评估
python deploy_sim.py --task_name=plate_out --num_demos=2 --num_rollouts=10

# Custom model path / 自定义模型路径
python deploy_sim.py --model_path=./runs/my_experiment --task_name=open_box --num_demos=3
```

**Available RLBench tasks / 可用的 RLBench 任务:**
plate_out, stack_blocks, open_box, close_box, phone_on_base, toilet_seat_down, etc. (see `sim_utils.py` for full list / 完整列表见 `sim_utils.py`)

### Data Generation / 数据生成

```bash
# Generate pseudo-demonstrations with validation set / 生成伪演示和验证集
python generate_pseudo_data.py --num_tasks=100 --val_tasks=10 --num_workers=4

# Visualize generated data / 可视化生成的数据
python visualize_pseudo_data_simple.py  # Simple visualization / 简单可视化
python visualize_pseudo_data.py         # Full visualization with animations / 完整可视化（含动画）
```

### Utilities / 工具脚本

```bash
# Quick start script (interactive) / 快速启动脚本（交互式）
./quick_start_shapenet.sh

# Checkpoint management / Checkpoint 管理
./manage_checkpoints.sh list <run_name>
./manage_checkpoints.sh prepare <run_name> <checkpoint>
./manage_checkpoints.sh clean <run_name> [keep_n]
```

