## File Organization / 文件组织

```
ip/                          # Core package / 核心包
├── models/                  # Model definitions / 模型定义
│   ├── diffusion.py         # GraphDiffusion (Lightning module)
│   ├── model.py             # AGI (main model / 主模型)
│   ├── graph_rep.py         # Graph representation / 图表示
│   ├── graph_transformer.py # Graph transformer / 图 Transformer
│   ├── scene_encoder.py     # Point cloud encoder / 点云编码器
│   └── occupancy_net.py     # Occupancy network (unused / 未使用)
├── utils/                   # Utilities / 工具
│   ├── shapenet_loader.py   # ShapeNet dataset loader / ShapeNet 数据集加载器
│   ├── pseudo_demo_generator.py  # Pseudo-demo generation / 伪演示生成
│   ├── continuous_dataset.py     # Continuous generation dataset / 连续生成数据集
│   ├── running_dataset.py        # Pre-generated data loader / 预生成数据加载器
│   ├── data_proc.py              # Data processing utilities / 数据处理工具
│   └── common_utils.py           # Common utilities / 通用工具
├── configs/                 # Configuration / 配置
│   └── base_config.py       # Base configuration / 基础配置
└── train.py                 # Training script (pre-generated data) / 训练脚本（预生成数据）

# Root level scripts / 根目录脚本
train_with_pseudo.py         # Training with continuous generation / 连续生成训练
generate_pseudo_data.py      # Batch pseudo-data generation / 批量伪数据生成
deploy_sim.py                # Simulation deployment / 仿真部署
sim_utils.py                 # Simulation utilities / 仿真工具
visualize_pseudo_data.py     # Data visualization / 数据可视化
quick_start_shapenet.sh      # Quick start script / 快速启动脚本
manage_checkpoints.sh        # Checkpoint management / Checkpoint 管理
```

